About the Position

The position will be responsible for:

Sampling of client sites in accordance with client requirements, including on-site field analyses where applicable;
Conducting equipment set up in outdoor area or at height;
Assisting with mobilization to and from site;
Ensuring the appropriate sampling equipment and approved methodology is used to provide a quality service to the clients;
Optimising turnaround times for samples whilst ensuring the highest quality of sampling protocol is achieved and maintained;
Understanding methodology changes that affect the operations of sampling;
Ensuring all sampling equipment are calibrated, kept correctly maintained as well as clean and tidy;
Maintaining an appearance both personally and reflected in equipment presentation, in accordance with the quality requirements of ALS;
Investigate options that increase productivity and efficiency through equipment upgrading or new technology;
Assisting with transfer of samples and data from field operations to base operations;
Batching in off all samples;
Prioritising of samples on the day of arrival into the laboratory;
Be prepared to work out of normal working hours and outside Hong Kong as required.

About you

To be successful in this role you will have:

Required Knowledge, Skills & Abilities:

Excellent communication skills, both written and oral;
Excellent quality service approach and attitude;
Solves basic problems;
Negotiation and conflict resolution skills;
Well presented;
Good physical fitness;
Able to work outdoor and at height;
Strong numerical skills;
Team orientated;
Attention to detail.

Required Qualifications:

A tertiary science qualification, preferably Chemistry or in other Science subjects (e.g. Higher Diploma or Degree)
0-1 years previous laboratory experience (Fresh graduate are welcome to apply)
Field work and sampling experience preferable but not required
Construction Industry Safety Training Certificate (Green Card), Working at Height Safety, Confined Spaces Training Certificate, or other training/certificate is an advantage;

